  "ftbquests.chapter.wu_qi.quest970201556921326311.subtitle": "Smithing from drops from defeating §6{entity.cataclysm.maledictus}§r.",
  "ftbquests.chapter.wu_qi.questC51C2F3266B0A59.subtitle": "Obtained by Smithing",
  "ftbquests.chapter.wu_qi.title": "§6Mysterious Weapons",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest44D2EB5EE8D3FEF8.description1": "&bThis modpack provides difficulty levels that can be adjusted at any time. Please choose the difficulty that suits you! And do not insult the author for choosing the wrong one.&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest44D2EB5EE8D3FEF8.description2": "&6When on a &eDedicated Server&6, only server operators can use this command!&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest44D2EB5EE8D3FEF8.description3": "For any hostile mob:",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest44D2EB5EE8D3FEF8.description4": "&aEasy&r: 0.6x &bAttack Damage&r, 0.8x &cHealth&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest44D2EB5EE8D3FEF8.description5": "&6Normal (Default)&r: 1x &bAttack Damage&r, 1x &cHealth&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest44D2EB5EE8D3FEF8.description6": "&4&lHard&r: 2x &bAttack Damage&r, 1.5x &cHealth&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest44D2EB5EE8D3FEF8.description7": "(Bosses within Infinite Samsara have slightly adjusted formulas)",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest44D2EB5EE8D3FEF8.subtitle": "Choose the appropriate difficulty, don't impose difficulty on yourself",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest44D2EB5EE8D3FEF8.title": "Global Difficulty Setting",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description1": "§6Discord: §dhttps://discord.gg/UfVF8b2GFk&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description10": "§bThe Sanctuary: El_mal（玩建造的牢E）, 300wan&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description11": "§bCustom AI: XVIII-ling, 气球恶魔&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description12": "§bCustom Animations: merlin204, asanginxst&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description13": "§bCustom Art: Ao， 一只路过的小吴，XVIII-ling\u0026r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description14": "§bAnd: All the excellent mod, resource pack, and shader pack authors",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description15": "——P1nero",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description2": "§6QQ Group 1: §d948180812",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description3": "Thanks to all the companions who have walked this path with me! Thanks to all the excellent mod authors! This is my second modpack. If you're interested in simulation management, you can try my other modpack:",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description4": "§a《SkilletMan》§r!",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description5": "The name 'The Casket of Reveries' was originally thought up by my friend. At that time, we planned to create a mod that would go down in history, but for some reasons we didn't make it to the end...",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description6": "§6《The Casket of Reveries》 means sealing beautiful things in an exquisite little box to slumber, just like the ruins we descended upon.§r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description7": "Friends who have played §a《SkilletMan》§r should know that I personally don't like cramming all quest storylines and interactions into the FTB interface. Therefore, in this modpack, FTB quests will play more of an encyclopedia role, gradually unlocking through interactions in the world. Our story development and item collection are mainly presented through NPC dialogues.",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description8": "I also don't like blindly piling up mods. The hostile boss mods used in the main storyline of this modpack are more suitable for interaction with Epic Fight. This modpack uses the latest Epic Fight, bringing you a brand-new Epic Fight experience, proving the great potential of Epic Fight.",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description9": "§bAcknowledgments:",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.subtitle": "\"Legend says there are ruins in the deep sea, watching over this world\"",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.task.325688042160411882.title": "This modpack is in the testing phase. The Sanctuary is still not complete, and some areas are locked (There really are no hidden treasure chests!)",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.task.3257333974082388709.title": "If no other chapters appear, go explore nearby～",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.task.8806221034708452812.title": "§6This modpack will not charge you any fees! It is only released on the CurseForge platform. Third-party distribution is strictly prohibited! Any third-party reposting (including using cloud drives) is an infringement! Welcome to report!§r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.title": "Author's Words",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest7487272814909384521.description1": "This modpack has the §b\"Fast TPA\"§r mod installed, enriching the multiplayer experience!",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest7487272814909384521.description2": "Press §6[Right ALT]§r by default to launch a distress signal!",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest7487272814909384521.description3": "You can customize the distress signal text and the text when going to assist.",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest7487272814909384521.subtitle": "\"{key.fast_tpa.category}\"",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest7487272814909384521.task.5950346987720516679.title": "{key.fast_tpa.category}",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest9DE1A548EA3F9BA.description1": "&bProgram：P1nero",
